# QA run outputs: keep run-plan.yaml, results.jsonl, report.md, and curated
# evidence, but ignore disposable fixture copies, temporary homes, caches, and
# external target sandboxes generated during execution.
docs/qa/runs/**/evidence/
docs/qa/runs/**/fixtures/
docs/qa/runs/**/qa-home/
docs/qa/runs/**/qa-*/
docs/qa/runs/**/outside-targets/
docs/qa/runs/**/tmp/
docs/qa/runs/**/temp/
